text: Elm Tree is a community in Central Frontenac, Ontario, Canada, between Arden and Kaladar. Many lakes in Elm Tree's vicinity are still quiet and undisturbed. The major lakes are Bull Lake, Buck Lake, Horseshoe Lake, Cranberry Lake; the Salmon River is also nearby. Many other lakes and creeks dot the landscape. Category:Communities in Frontenac County
title: Elm Tree, Ontario
